mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.mvncmd.example -

DartifactId=myapp -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart -

DinteractiveMode=false
• mvn compile : This will compile the source code.

• mvn test : This will run unit tests

• mvn package : Package the project into a JAR

• Run Application : java -cp target/myapp-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar 

com.example.App


gradle –type java-application

gradle build

gradle run 

Build and Run Maven Project

Navigate to Project Path and Run Maven Project.

Mvn compile

Mvn package

Java -cp package name path name

Initialize Gradle

• Navigate to Project Path and Initialize Gradle. Use Commands → gradle init

• It will ask Found a Maven build. Generate a Gradle build from this? (default: yes) [yes, 

no] → Type Yes

• Select Groovy as build Script

Type Yes for Generate build using new APIs
